<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="39" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="39">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="39">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Koch" authorityYear="1936" class="Insecta" family="Hepialidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena araxis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="araxis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="39">Zygaena araxis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a valid species. According to Hofmann and Tremewan (2020) its taxonomic status has a confusing history. It was raised to species level by 
<bibRefCitation author="Goergner, E" journalOrPublisher="Entomofauna" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" pagination="33 - 54" refId="B29" refString="Goergner, E, Hofmann, A, 1982. Eine neue Zygaenenart fuer die Tuerkei (Lepidoptera; Zygaenidae, Zygaena Fabricius, 1775, Subgenus Mesembrynus Huebner, [1819]). Entomofauna 3: 33 - 54" title="Eine neue Zygaenenart fuer die Tuerkei (Lepidoptera; Zygaenidae, Zygaena Fabricius, 1775, Subgenus Mesembrynus Huebner, [1819])." volume="3" year="1982">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Görgner">Goergner</normalizedToken>
and Hofmann (1982)
</bibRefCitation>
, but subsequently placed as a subspecies to 
<taxonomicName genus="Z." lsidName="Z. rubricollis" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" rank="species" species="rubricollis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="39">Z. rubricollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Hampson, 1900 by 
<bibRefCitation author="Hofmann, A" journalOrPublisher="Harley Books, Colchester" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" refId="B25" refString="Hofmann, A, Tremewan, WG, 1996. A Systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae). Harley Books, Colchester" title="A Systematic Catalogue of the Zygaeninae (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae)." year="1996">Hofmann and Tremewan (1996)</bibRefCitation>
. Finally, it was reinstated as a valid species by 
<bibRefCitation author="Keil, T" journalOrPublisher="Nota Lepidopterologica" pageId="0" pageNumber="39" refId="B31" refString="Keil, T, 2003. Attend [sic] for a new classification of the taxa around Zygaena rubricollis Hampson, 1900 (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae, Zygaeninae). Abstracts of the VIII International Symposium on Zygaenidae, Dresden - Germany, 10-14 September 2003: 31-32." title="Attend [sic] for a new classification of the taxa around Zygaena rubricollis Hampson, 1900 (Lepidoptera: Zygaenidae, Zygaeninae). Abstracts of the VIII International Symposium on Zygaenidae, Dresden - Germany, 10 - 14 September 2003: 31 - 32." year="2003">Keil (2003)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
